gomodel:SYNGO_3015  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.3: \"CPEB-1 regulates c-Jun RNA translation\"\n\nFig.4: \"Analysis of GH-induced LTP\"\n- \" Bath application of recombinant human GH (22 ng/ml) onto slices elicits LTP in wild-type and CPEB-1 KO mice. Note that, at 90-120 min, the amplitude of the LTP in KO animals is 55% of that in the wild-type animals (n = 5 each for wild type and KO).\". Experimental description: - \"CPEB-1 KO mice (Tay and Richter, 2001) ...\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
